1
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,560
Extra! Extra!

2
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:29,160
Qing and Japan signed the Treaty of Shimonoseki,

3
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,280
ceding Taiwan, Penghu, and Liaodong,

4
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,720
and paying an indemnity of 200 million taels!

5
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,560
Shameless!

6
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,479
The court is incompetent,

7
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:37,280
signing this humiliating treaty!

8
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,960
Linglong.

9
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,840
Elders.

10
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:52,720
Elders.

11
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,490
What you said before

12
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,200
about me taking the Hu family seal

13
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,520
and succeeding as the head of the family,

14
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,680
does it still count?

15
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,040
It does.

16
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,400
Of course it does.

17
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,840
The Hu family seal.

18
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,220
I have already brought it out.

19
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,280
Come,

20
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,000
pay respects to the ancestors.

21
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:17,160
May the ancestors of the clan bear witness.

22
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:20,760
Hu Linglong, the 58th generation descendant of the Hu family,

23
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:22,880
succeeds the lineage,

24
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:25,040
and receives the seal to lead the clan.

25
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,940
The ceremony is complete.

26
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,120
Elders,

27
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,760
I want to use this handover of the clan seal

28
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,220
to convene a clan meeting.

29
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,320
We recently heard the shocking news

30
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,040
that Lushun suffered a brutal massacre.

31
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,720
The whole nation is in mourning,

32
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,580
and mourning banners are hung all over the country.

33
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,480
But today,

34
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,360
the Hu family ancestral hall will not hang mourning banners,

35
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,820
but only set up tea tables.

36
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:17,810
We will use tea instead of blood to pay tribute to the unjustly killed in Liaodong.

37
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,200
Today,

38
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,680
I have gathered all the Hu family members at the ancestral hall

39
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:24,740
just to invite everyone here to taste three cups of tea.

40
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,880
This is from the Hu family's tea warehouse,

41
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,160
treasured for many years,

42
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:31,020
the Qianlong tribute tea, Tunlu.

43
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,280
Although it has the honorable name of tribute tea,

44
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,680
because it has been sealed for so many years,

45
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:37,010
it has long since become moldy and rotten.

46
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:41,760
Everyone,

47
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,930
please taste it.

48
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,440
The appearance of this tea

49
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,770
and the taste of this tea

50
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,240
are just like today's China,

51
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,160
enjoying a reputation in vain,

52
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,220
but rotten inside.

53
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,160
The blood of our compatriots in Port Arthur

54
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:57,280
has a stronger stench than this rotten tea.

55
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,800
The dignity of our Heavenly Dynasty

56
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,800
is cheaper than the scum in this cup.

57
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,530
Being conservative

58
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,040
is waiting for death.

59
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,480
Refusing to change

60
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,940
is digging our own graves.

61
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,540
This cup of tea,

62
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:11,240
I call it 'conservatism leads to ruin'.

63
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,560
This saucer of tea

64
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,890
is poorly made and full of impurities.

65
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,130
In our Hu family,

66
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,320
this kind of tea is either fed to pigs and dogs,

67
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,850
or scattered in the fields.

68
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,520
But do you know

69
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,480
where it came from?

70
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,880
I bought it from foreigners at a high price.

71
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,060
Please taste it again.

72
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:41,720
This tea

73
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,820
was crushed by foreign machines.

74
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,000
This tea

75
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,330
was presented by flattering compradors.

76
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,680
Our current China

77
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,560
is like this crushed tea.

78
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,800
Our land is shattered and on the verge of destruction.

79
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:56,560
Look at the tea dregs at the bottom of the cup.

80
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,200
Doesn't it look like the streets of Lushun,

81
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:02,240
littered with the severed limbs of our compatriots hacked by Japanese swords?

82
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,280
This cup of tea,

83
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,520
I call it the tragedy of a fallen nation.

84
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,360
This last saucer of tea

85
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:17,160
is Keemun black tea improved by me.

86
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,360
Developing this tea

87
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,880
has been full of hardships and twists and turns.

88
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,540
But now that it is successful,

89
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,320
we were supposed to go to the West for the exposition,

90
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,920
but were hindered by assassination attempts.

91
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,440
Everyone, please

92
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,760
taste this last cup.

93
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,290
Encountering such things,

94
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,730
I now understand

95
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,960
that even if China is full of treasures

96
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,159
and talented people,

97
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:56,159
if we do not drive out foreign invaders,

98
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,760
our vast land

99
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,820
will one day be completely trampled.

100
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,760
The danger of being plundered is imminent.

101
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:04,800
Therefore,

102
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,280
we must seek new methods

103
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,760
and reform to become stronger,

104
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:10,440
to protect our foundation and enrich our nation,

105
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,640
so as to avoid the peril of subjugation.

106
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,580
This cup of tea,

107
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,800
I call it the spirit of innovation.

108
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,360
Everyone,

109
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,080
at this moment of national crisis,

110
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,760
with foreigners causing chaos,

111
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:24,760
the Hu family is willing to lead by example,

112
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:27,360
establish new methods and implement new rules.

113
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,280
From now on,

114
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,160
the profits from the Hu family's tea shop

115
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,920
will all be used for the education and advancement of our clan's youth.

116
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,960
Those who like literature should devote themselves to study,

117
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:37,040
and those who like martial arts should focus on training,

118
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:40,120
all to protect our home, defend our country, and expel the enemy.

119
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,000
The Hu family is willing to give everything we have,

120
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,200
without hesitation.

121
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,280
The flame of China,

122
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,570
we must strive to be strong.

123
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,280
The flame of China,

124
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,600
we must strive to be strong.

125
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,320
How did I get back?

126
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,720
Linglong.

127
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,600
Qiao Xin.

128
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,400
You are...

129
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:43,640
Stop!

130
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:55,600
Qiao Xin,

131
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,320
are you alright?

132
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,040
Yijun.

133
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,680
Qiao Xin,

134
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,610
does your wound still hurt?

135
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:05,690
Not anymore.

136
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,440
Right,

137
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,520
Qiao Xin.

138
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,160
After I got your call that night,

139
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,080
I saw you severely injured on the ground

140
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,320
and took you to the hospital.

141
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,640
I didn't expect that after you woke up,

142
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,720
you'd rush to the ancestral house

143
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,440
and run into the person who attacked you.

144
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,200
That person

145
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:20,080
is a spy trying to steal the tea seeds.

146
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,480
The new black tea you cultivated

147
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,280
has received unanimous praise from the judges.

148
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,240
Excuse me, how soon will this new tea

149
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,480
be officially launched?

150
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,640
The team is currently carrying out

151
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,920
final quality control.

152
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:30,650
We will let everyone taste it as soon as possible.

153
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,460
President,

154
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,760
I will definitely find a way to get

155
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,890
their new tea seeds,

156
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,960
at all costs.

157
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,559
Qiao Xin.

158
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,000
When you're healed,

159
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,370
I will go with you

160
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,600
no matter what you want to find

161
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,860
or where you want to go.

162
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,280
Yijun.

163
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,640
Do you believe in time travel?

164
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,080
When I was unconscious,

165
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,360
I seemed to have time-traveled

166
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,200
to the Hu family in Qimen in 1894.

167
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:57,360
I also met someone named Hu Linglong.

168
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,400
We became good friends there

169
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:02,730
and experienced a lot of things together.

170
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,040
Thrilling,

171
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,040
interesting,

172
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,490
and unforgettable.

173
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:09,180
It was truly more wonderful than a TV series.

174
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:11,320
Miss,

175
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:13,040
why are you here?

176
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,120
Do you know me?

177
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,220
My name is Qiao Xin.

178
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,010
Do you know Hu Linglong?

179
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:18,560
Hu Linglong.

180
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,490
You are Qiao Xin?

181
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,400
I waited.

182
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,520
I finally waited for you.

183
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,720
I'm the fifth-generation ancestral hall keeper of the Hu family.

184
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:28,160
Following the dying wish of my ancestor Hu Linglong,

185
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:30,290
she asked me to give this letter to her.

186
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,440
This...

187
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,370
is a letter left by Linglong for me.

188
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,080
It's all true.

189
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,760
My friend Qiao Xin,

190
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,820
seeing this letter is like seeing me.

191
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,980
Since the danger at the pier that day,

192
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,960
the jade pendant was destroyed,

193
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,560
and I have heard nothing from you.

194
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,690
I miss you very much.

195
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,000
I don't know if you have returned to heaven

196
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,600
and rejoined the immortals.

197
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:57,840
If so,

198
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,170
my heart can be at peace.

199
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:02,320
Although this letter cannot be delivered to you,

200
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,560
tonight my thoughts are surging,

201
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,760
and I can't sleep.

202
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,530
I pick up my pen to write,

203
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:08,560
treating it as pouring out my heart

204
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,620
to comfort myself.

205
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,680
Since my mother left,

206
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,240
I often dream of her.

207
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,320
Whenever I think

208
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,380
of the situation when she died for me,

209
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:23,730
I still feel as if my heart is being twisted by a knife.

210
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,160
In life,

211
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,440
meetings and partings are common,

212
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,160
and regrets of missing out are many.

213
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,160
In just a few months,

214
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,820
I have deeply felt this truth.

215
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:36,040
My parents, Zhinian, and you,

216
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,090
are all my regrets in this life.

217
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,420
The meeting between you and me

218
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:42,240
was bestowed by fate,

219
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,600
seeming real yet illusionary.

220
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,280
Even if I tell Uncle Zhao,

221
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,980
he won't fully believe it.

222
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:50,040
Although I was raised as a boy since childhood,

223
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:52,800
my temperament is still inferior and cowardly.

224
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,680
Fortunately, over the past few months,

225
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,360
with you by my side day and night,

226
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:58,120
I was able to break out of the cocoon and free myself,

227
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,980
facing all difficulties calmly.

228
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,000
Now that we have parted,

229
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,930
I know it will be hard to meet again.

230
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,920
However, even if a thousand sails pass by,

231
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,720
I am still willing to wait for you to come back here.

232
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,680
Half a year ago,

233
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,480
Zhinian sacrificed his life for the country

234
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,280
and shed his blood on the battlefield.

235
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,520
Before Zhinian left,

236
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:18,040
I parted with him in a hurry,

237
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,560
which unexpectedly became our final farewell.

238
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:21,080
The promise we made that day

239
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,560
can no longer be fulfilled.

240
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,640
It still breaks my heart,

241
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,500
and I can't forget it day or night.

242
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:27,840
Zhinian and I

243
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,960
are not meant to be in this life,

244
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:32,290
and can only continue our fate in the next.

245
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:35,720
Qiao Xin.

246
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,960
For some reason,

247
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,440
when I'm with you,

248
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,520
I always feel an inexplicable closeness,

249
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,560
as if we knew each other in a previous life.

250
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:45,520
I know deities are immortal,

251
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:48,180
while I, a mortal, will eventually turn to dust.

252
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:50,720
I still wish to leave this letter in the ancestral hall,

253
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,880
and have instructed the caretakers to pass it down through generations,

254
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,040
endlessly.

255
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:56,600
When you return to the mortal realm one day,

256
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:59,640
you can retrieve this letter and relive old memories.

257
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:00,560
Your close friend, Linglong.

258
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,620
Written in person.

259
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,480
Linglong,

260
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,210
you were such a wonderful girl.

261
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,720
It's a pity that fate always toys with the unfortunate.

262
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,400
It's a pity you were born in the wrong era.

263
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,640
The land of China today

264
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:12,080
is completely different from the past.

265
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,200
The society is stable,

266
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,200
with abundant food and clothing,

267
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,480
and the people live in peace and contentment.

268
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,440
No outsiders dare to bully us anymore.

269
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,960
If only you could see this,

270
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,420
how wonderful it would be.

271
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,320
Qiao Xin,

272
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,720
you're awake.

273
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,360
You slept for a long time.

274
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,320
Seeing you just recovered,

275
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,800
I didn't want to disturb you.

276
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,760
Are we going anywhere else?

277
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,320
No need.

278
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,170
Whether it's true or false,

279
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,040
I already have the answer in my heart.
